    * fix for HB_OS_WIN_32 when DIRECTORY("D:\*.*","V") -> pointer overflow.
      because in function GetOldesFile(), szFileName was passed instead of
      szPath while memory allocated only 7 bytes, just enough for "C:\*.*"

